resources.string: Bu uygulama servisin dokunma özelliğini kullanır

Turn ON the switch on top right. The app only uses the click functionality of the service to automate the swiping in Tinder.

Note:
You may receive a warning after turning this screen. You may safely ignore that, as AutoSwipe doesn't collect any of your personal information.
